mbedTLS vendored library placeholder.
Used for TLS in the HTTP client (rivet::net).

Populate with the official release:
  https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls/releases

Expected layout after populating:
  include/mbedtls/
    ssl.h, net_sockets.h, entropy.h, ctr_drbg.h, x509_crt.h, ...
  library/
    *.c files from the mbedtls library/ directory

